  "releases": [
    {
      "title": "v3.51.1",
      "description": "- A significant performance boost was achieved for large Taskfiles (monorepos) by skipping templating altogether when the string is static (#2820 by @romnn).\r\n- Added `absPath` template function that resolves a path to its absolute form, cleaning `..` and `.` components (#2681, #2788 by @mateenanjum).\r\n- Added `joinEnv` function to join paths based on your oprating system: `;` for Windows and `:` elsewhere, and `joinUrl` to join URL paths. Also, added two new special variables: `FILE_PATH_SEPARATOR` which returns `\\` on Windows and `/` elsewhere, and `PATH_LIST_SEPARATOR` which returns `;` on Windows and `:` elsewhere (#2406, #2408 by @solvingj).\r\n- Update the shell interpreter with a regression fix (#2812, #2832 by @andreynering).\r\n- Fix potential panic with the shell interpreter (#2810 by @trulede).",
